issues.fix:
Replace the two separate set calls with a single functional setState that revokes the prior URL:

// Before
setReceiptFile(file);
setPreviewUrl(URL.createObjectURL(file));

// After
setReceiptFile(file);
setPreviewUrl((prev) => {
  if (prev) URL.revokeObjectURL(prev);
  return URL.createObjectURL(file);
});

